        <h2 class="featurette-heading"><img class="api-image" src="img/dev-sm.svg">Accounts Resource</h2>
        <p class="lead"></p>
        <p>The account resource is listed at the base url. This resource contains information about your account as well as links to the pertinent resources you have access to.</p>
        <h4>Request:</h4>
        <p class="well">GET https://api.messageradius.com/</p>
        <p>Request the <code>base</code> url; the account is contained in the root document.</p>
        <h4>Response:</h4>
        <p class="well">{<br>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"account_id": "5034fe38639184d116000001",<br>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"name": "Radius Networks",<br>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"links": {<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"subscriptions": { "href": "https://api.messageradius.com/api/subscriptions" },<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"beacons": { "href": "https://api.messageradius.com/api/beacons" }<br>
  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<br>
}</p>
<h4>Example:</h4>
<p class="well">$ mr-curl "https://api.messageraidus.com/"</p>

